<title>Aw Pathien Na Min Lien Hen</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Thilsiem chung Pathien Min zanglawi bang thang hen,
 Simlei nam tinin zailan chawi-an hen la
 Aw Lalpa, Na thilsiem te hi vang hun pie'n
 Na ma ah ka hun lan ui.

[V2]
 Thilsiem chung Pathien zaitha hat vangin
 Thaithak sakmel kipahum I mu tau ie
 Chawian un Lalpa a lien a neute haw
 Aw Pathien, Na min lien hen.

[V3]
 2. A lien a neu lungtuok na Thilsiem Pathien
 Thang hen la, lien hen, Na min kawl kimvel ah
 Enkawl in, Aw chung Pathien, Na thilsiem te,
 Sing zatam guo bang hinna'n.

[V4]
 3. Zaila leh thimthu'n chawian un, Lal Minlun,
 A thilsiem haw gen vielun, kawl kimvel ah;
 Van nuoi mi zatam guo bang I hinna di'n,
 Chawian un, Lalpa Pathien.</lyrics>
</song>